'''Boyd Rankin''' is a weapon smith and armorer. He is a co-founder of the company Irish Arms. He is a senior supervising armorer for the [[Season 1|first]] and [[Season 2|second]] season of ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. He plays [[Mikken]] in the first season.
